Package extended_mitre.cwe

Class CWEcategoryObj

  • java.lang.Object
    • extended_mitre.cwe.CWEcategoryObj
  • public class CWEcategoryObj
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a CWE category object (CWE category id, category name attribute, category status attribute, category summary attribute, relationship objects (CWE ID, view ID), external reference reference objects)

    It can create a CWE category object from given parameters and return it

    It also can go through an XML file with CWE weaknesses or CAPEC objects, find category objects, parse them into CWE category objects and return them

    Author:
    Tomas Bozek (XarfNao)

    • Method Detail

      • CWEcategoryToArrayList

        public static java.util.List<CWEcategoryObj> CWEcategoryToArrayList​(java.lang.String file,
                                                                    java.util.List<CWEextRefObj> ext_refs)
        This method's purpose is to go through an XML file with CWE weaknesses or CAPEC objects, find category objects, parse them into CWE category objects and return them, deprecated ones not included

        It uses DOM XML parser

        If it can't find any informations, it returns these attributes as null values

        Parameters:
        file - path to an XML file which will be parsed from
        ext_refs - existing External Reference objects for search of the relating ones
        Returns:
        list of parsed CWE category objects
